songs.title: Jungle
songs.lyrics:
[From Remix]

[Verse 1]
You’re beautiful with golden hair and black eyes
But you’re alone, you’re in the cold
So you hide

[Chorus]
Young hearts, run free
Let our inhibitions be swinging through the vine trees
Young hearts, run free
You can drive me crazy, baby, baby

[Refrain]
I want to
You want to
I want to
You want to

[Verse 2]
You’re beautiful with golden hair
But you’re alone, you’re in the cold
Young hearts run free
Young hearts run free

[Refrain]
To the jungle
To the jungle

[Verse 3]
Oh, this could be our starting out, our wild lives
And as the wind blows through your hair, you’ll find
Young hearts run free
Young hearts run free

[Refrain]
To the jungle
To the jungle
To the jungle

[Bridge]
I want to
You want to
I want to
You want to

[Refrain]
Go to the jungle
To the jungle
